Package com.hert.legacyofat.backend

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionPerform
    Interface for all objects that can perform() (Items and Actions)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    Class for actions, which are things used by characters in the battle activity.
    Battle
    Class for receiving battle data for the main menu from the backend.
    Chara
    Class for a character, used throughout the game in various places.
    Guser
    The Guser of backend, this static class holds all the data from the backend.
    Item
    Class for an item, used throughout the game by characters in various places.
    ItemPayload
    Class for sending character item data from the main menu to the backend.
    Team
    Class for a team, which is a container of 4 characters used in battles.
